  "DescIdentified": {
    "type": "cexolocstring",
    "value": {
      "0": "This magical shield is imbued with properties befitting a worshipper of Helm, and its use is limited to those of lawful neutral alignment.\n\nThe god of guardians and protectors, Helm is the epitome of the guardian, the watcher, and has in years past been\ngreatly venerated by those who need to remain watchful for evil at their doorsteps. Helm is ever-vigilant, and embodies the spirit of lawful neutrality. Helm's Symbol is an open eye painted onto a gauntlet.\n\nHelm teaches that one must be ever vigilant, ever aware, ever prepared for one's enemies. He also serves who stands and waits and watches carefully. Careful planning will always defeat rushed actions in the end."
    }
  },
